caption: They suck! I don't see this business lasting long. Hook & Reel is much better. 1st time was a problem. 2nd and last time 3/30/21 even worse. I'm done. I refuse to give my money to people that have a problem with me.

Tried food from here a few times, it was all tasty, not traditional cajun, more like a cajun- asian spot, but foods good. Had lunch there for a co workers birthday a couple days ago, service was mehh, but understandable considering COVID, the staff is 1 counter person do it all besides the kitchen staff....the seafood broils are good, don't like their crawfish, assuming its frozen for months, shrimp, mussels & calamari was good, Catfish Po boy was very delicious! Seafood fried rice as well. I would definitely recommend trying their food!

Great flavor and generous portions! We ordered a family meal and the delivery was so fast the seafood was still steaming. We had a little leftover after splitting between 2 of us, if you’re splitting between more, I’d recommend adding rice or a side to soak up the extra sauce. Mild level of spice is very mild, so level up if you’re a spice fan.  5 stars all around, will definitely be ordering again!
Everything was so fresh and delicious. The shrimp were large and so tasty. The serving sizes were generous. Highly recommend!!!!
We’ve ordered twice from Crab Dynasty, and we’ve loved every single thing we’ve had. I love seafood, and this place definitely hits the spot.

I had the shrimp basket with garlic broccoli. The shrimp was good, but I won’t mind to taste some Cajun spice. I can careless about the salad that came with the shrimp basket. I asked to not over fried the dynasty wings, and it was done right. The girl was very helpful recommending the mango hahanero sauce to go with the wings, love it. I will definitely be back.

Excellent bang for the buck! The seafood and non-seafood items were hot, fresh, and flavorful. I recommend trying their Dynasty Blend sauce for a seafood combo. Prices were very fair given the generous portion sizes. They're very fast -- food was ready to pick up 15 min after ordering. I was also happy to see the premises looked very clean, and that they had a large shield to protect the staff behind the register. Really happy they joined the neighborhood!
The crab and lobster with the garlic butter old bay was amazing! So happy this is now open!
